me":"2018-10-08T09:38:38.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"c99c63e9feee976ab4ec2d6a05a7b054cb281ba9","tid":852986,"uid":27363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:43:39.000Z","msg":"存款準備金率都未到0%<br />\n仲有排贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfdac1355eda3dbaa7acb1c5c0238518102ffba","tid":852986,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:43:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83e467da964ccd83ea1bc19cf1b1295e705780e","tid":852986,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:45:01.000Z","msg":"【人行降準】人民幣貶值幅度持續擴大 離岸跌穿6.93 (16:44)<br />\n<br />\n文章日期：2018年10月8日<br />\n<br />\n在岸及離岸人民幣貶值幅度持續擴大，離岸人民幣跌至6.9369，貶值419點子，進一步逼近今年8月15日的高位6.9586；而在岸人民幣貶值幅度亦擴大，最多貶值470點子，報6.9158，逼近8月15日的高位6.9376<br />\n<br />\n救市成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}